##### Common Mistakes and Fixes

| Mistake | Why It Fails | Fix |
|---------|--------------|-----|
| `cargo test` with `working_dir: "."` but Cargo.toml in `loom/` | Command runs in wrong directory | Set `working_dir: "loom"` |
| `grep -q 'pattern' src/file.rs` but file created in `loom/src/` | Path doesn't exist relative to working_dir | Use `grep -q 'pattern' loom/src/file.rs` OR set `working_dir: "loom"` |
| `test -f new-feature.rs` | Missing directory prefix | Use `test -f src/new-feature.rs` |
| `./target/debug/myapp --help` | target/ may be in subdirectory | Use full path: `./loom/target/debug/myapp --help` |
| `npm test` in monorepo | Package.json in subdirectory | Set `working_dir: "packages/app"` |

